with src ( ELA_DIMNSN_ID, ctrct_sub_option_code, ctrct_sub_option_code_dscr, ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, lic_agrmt_type_code, lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord, add_date, add_by_hrcl_name, mod_date, mod_by_hrcl_name ) as (select -1, l.ctrct_sub_option_code, COALESCE(c1.code_dscr, '') as ctrct_sub_option_code_dscr, l.ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, l.lic_agrmt_type_code, COALESCE(c2.code_dscr, '') as lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, l.lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord, l.add_date, l.add_by_hrcl_name, l.mod_date, l.mod_by_hrcl_name
from rnwl2.ctrct_sub_option_lic_agrmt_lnk l left join shar2.code_dscr c1 on l.ctrct_sub_option_code = c1.code and c1.col_name = 'ctrct_sub_option_code' and c1.inact_flag = 0 left join shar2.code_dscr c2 on l.lic_agrmt_type_code = c2.code and c2.col_name = 'lic_agrmt_type_code' and c2.inact_flag = 0 where l.inact_flag = 0
union all
select 0 as ELA_DIMNSN_ID, cast('UNKNOWN' as char(8)) as ctrct_sub_option_code, 'Unknown' as code_dscr, 99 as ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, cast('NONEL' as char(6)) as lic_agrmt_type_code, 'Non-ELA' as lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, 2 as lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord, COALESCE(d.ADD_DATE, Current Timestamp), COALESCE(d.ADD_BY_HRCL_NAME, '#$HRCL_NAME#'), COALESCE(d.MOD_DATE, Current Timestamp), COALESCE(d.MOD_BY_HRCL_NAME, '#$HRCL_NAME#') from SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1 left join RNWL1.ELA_DIMNSN d on d.ctrct_sub_option_code = 'UNKNOWN' )
select COALESCE(d.ELA_DIMNSN_ID, s.ELA_DIMNSN_ID) as ELA_DIMNSN_ID, s.ctrct_sub_option_code, s.ctrct_sub_option_code_dscr, s.ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, s.lic_agrmt_type_code, s.lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, s.lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord, 0, m.MAX_ID, COALESCE(d.ADD_DATE, s.ADD_DATE), COALESCE(d.ADD_BY_HRCL_NAME, s.ADD_BY_HRCL_NAME), s.MOD_DATE, s.MOD_BY_HRCL_NAME from src s left join RNWL1.ELA_DIMNSN d on s.ctrct_sub_option_code = d.ctrct_sub_option_code, (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(ELA_DIMNSN_ID), 0) AS MAX_ID FROM RNWL1.ELA_DIMNSN) as m order by COALESCE(d.ELA_DIMNSN_ID, s.ELA_DIMNSN_ID), s.ctrct_sub_option_code with ur;
IF Trim(out.CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_CODE) = 'UNKNOWN' then DSJobStartTimestamp else out.MOD_DATE
IF out.ELA_DIMNSN_ID = -1 Then out.MAX_ID + @OUTROWNUM else out.ELA_DIMNSN_ID

CREATE TABLE DWDM1.ELA_DIMNSN ( ELA_DIMNSN_ID INTEGER NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_UI_ORD SMALLINT, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE CHAR(6) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_UI_ORD SMALLINT, INACT_FLAG SMALLINT NOT NULL, MOD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, MOD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL , PRIMARY KEY (ELA_DIMNSN_ID) )

CREATE TABLE DWDM1.ELA_DIMNSN ( ELA_DIMNSN_ID INTEGER NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_CODE CHAR(8) NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_UI_ORD SMALLINT, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE CHAR(6) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_UI_ORD SMALLINT, INACT_FLAG SMALLINT NOT NULL, ADD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, ADD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL, MOD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, MOD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL , PRIMARY KEY (ELA_DIMNSN_ID) )

CREATE TABLE DWDM1.ELA_DIMNSN ( ELA_DIMNSN_ID INTEGER NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, CTRCT_SUB_OPTION_UI_ORD SMALLINT, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE CHAR(6) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_CODE_DSCR VARCHAR(40) NOT NULL, LIC_AGRMNT_TYPE_UI_ORD SMALLINT, INACT_FLAG SMALLINT NOT NULL, MOD_DATE TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, MOD_BY_USER_NAME CHAR(12) NOT NULL , PRIMARY KEY (ELA_DIMNSN_ID) )

with src ( ctrct_sub_option_code, ctrct_sub_option_code_dscr, ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, lic_agrmt_type_code, lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord ) as (select l.ctrct_sub_option_code, COALESCE(c1.code_dscr, '') as ctrct_sub_option_code_dscr, l.ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, l.lic_agrmt_type_code, COALESCE(c2.code_dscr, '') as lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, l.lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord
from rnwl2.ctrct_sub_option_lic_agrmt_lnk l left join shar2.code_dscr c1 on l.ctrct_sub_option_code = c1.code and c1.col_name = 'ctrct_sub_option_code' and c1.inact_flag = 0 left join shar2.code_dscr c2 on l.lic_agrmt_type_code = c2.code and c2.col_name = 'lic_agrmt_type_code' and c2.inact_flag = 0 where l.inact_flag = 0
union all
select 'UNKNOWN' as ctrct_sub_option_code, 'Unknown' as code_dscr, 99 as ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord, 'UNKN' as lic_agrmt_type_code, 'Unknown' as lic_agrmt_type_code_dscr, 99 as lic_agrmt_type_ui_ord from SYSIBM.SYSDUMMY1 )
select COALESCE(d.ELA_DIMNSN_ID, -1) as ELA_DIMNSN_ID, s.*, m.* from src s left join RNWL1.ELA_DIMNSN d on s.ctrct_sub_option_code = d.ctrct_sub_option_code, (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(ELA_DIMNSN_ID), -1) AS MAX_ID FROM RNWL1.ELA_DIMNSN) as m order by case when s.ctrct_sub_option_code = 'UNKNOWN' then 0 else 1 end, s.ctrct_sub_option_ui_ord with ur;
